the arity of the circuit: the number of input qudits it acts on\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"c4068f8e-0d53-474c-bd28-6fead29d80cf"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "889f200f-fb47-45fd-b020-4bb5e7b4b4fd"], Cell[TextData[Cell[
