     BoxData["\"\<QiskitCircuit\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
      "4b60c14e-e050-48d2-b3fa-8a5249dfd529"],
     " or ",
     Cell[
     BoxData["\"\<Qiskit\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
      "3d21ca16-ae84-4bf2-a832-1825acfd6bb3"]
    }], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"2bb1afaf-12bd-409a-b08a-638b71711b5d"], 
    Cell["\<\
the corresponding circuit in Qiskit (note you need Python as external \
evaluator for this property)\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"d4d488ce-d675-41ab-a16c-a002d6132953"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "39545a10-5f22-445d-a713-8e53b77185c4"], Cell[TextData[{
     Cell[
     BoxData["\"\<Shift\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
      "5a76073b-1bd3-4103-aaaa-8be57f2450b2"],
     ",",
     StyleBox["n", "TI"]
    }], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"d6c11279-bf03-4854-9044-bd3cdd7f96be"], 
    Cell[TextData[{
     "shift the order of the circuit (the qudits it acts on) by ",
     StyleBox["n", "TI"]
    }], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"2296bca8-348d-480d-8447-4a6c1529e2f8"]}
  }]], "2ColumnTableMod",ExpressionUUID->"7d4ae3f0-4cc9-4c16-80ab-\
a2110e2ea97b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "There are many named-circuits, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   ButtonBox["QuantumCircuitOperator",
    BaseStyle->"Link",
    ButtonData->"paclet:Wolfram/QuantumFramework/ref/QuantumCircuitOperator"],
    "[", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"\"\<\!\(\*StyleBox[\"circuitname\", \"TI\"]\)\>\"", ",", "..."}],
     "}"}], "]"}]], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
  "a9aaad3c-e462-4d27-8cd4-b74a81b6633d"],
 ", for example, Bell, Toffoli, Grover (and its many oracles), quantum phase \
estimation, quantum fourier transform, Bernstein-Vazirani algorithm (and its \
many oracles), Graph and etc."
}], "Notes",ExpressionUUID->"72996b22-051a-40b8-8a27-f7a3c570eb2b"],

Cell[BoxData[GridBox[{
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "66b59dfe-e125-4d1b-a0d0-79604b5cb7fd"], Cell["", "TableText",
     FontWeight->Bold,ExpressionUUID->"0a149030-33bc-40d8-b111-ec9d5cca863b"],
     Cell["", "TableText",
     FontWeight->Bold,ExpressionUUID->"4b31b8ea-e9e7-4a42-b061-9f1e2c239525"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "32d26bda-8be8-41b0-9e14-5f4446edc45f"], Cell[TextData[Cell[
    BoxData["\"\<Bell\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
     "474f283a-0e2d-4969-81e0-abc10a8b8b85"]], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->
     "8611e7bd-4c03-490f-a686-bc552ad55f2e"], Cell["\<\
Bell-state preparation circuit ({H, CNOT}); prepares a Bell pair from the \
all-zeros state\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"ee8d8d3b-224b-4b8e-813a-6362618623ef"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "f89da1a7-4f23-49e1-a7b4-4e1e32685538"], Cell[TextData[Cell[BoxData[
     RowBox[{"\"\<GHZ\>\"", "[", "n", "]"}]], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
     "5d6eeb06-676c-4395-b1db-df80258d8ac6"]], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->
     "6e3bb4a5-9ddf-476e-a698-efb70a86cbdc"], Cell["\<\
preparation circuit for the n-qubit GHZ state (H, then a CNOT chain)\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"7461339d-9638-4c3d-b8e4-6ebbd29e58b3"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
