    }], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"577df0de-0c48-40fa-ab92-ea7ddf4a2330"], 
    Cell["\<\
a circuit that prepares the quantum state qs (qubit states via the \
multiplexer / RZY decomposition, general qudits via a block-diagonal \
construction)\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"a1ebce1b-58ba-410c-aaa6-01e39d1e445b"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "a836a8a7-9d2a-407c-b05c-b397de12dcdf"], Cell[TextData[Cell[BoxData[
