     "582d6465-3cbe-447f-b687-44a50c7f10f3"], Cell["\<\
encodes the integer n as a computational basis state (X gates on the 1-bits \
of n)\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"512c70fc-b33f-4025-9e4f-7819d81af75b"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "7bbbab32-87a2-48b3-9d49-4f46d62c04cb"], Cell[TextData[Cell[BoxData[
