     "4d520545-94d8-40ae-9107-857f27c06fda"], Cell["\<\
Toffoli (CCNOT) gate as a Clifford+T decomposition (15 gates)\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"90daf2bc-d8f3-4308-8186-abaea4825a9d"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
