 CellLabel->
  "Out[10]= ",ExpressionUUID->"d868beb9-1b69-4e8b-923b-5686f3c1d66a"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
The number of phase-estimation qubits (the 3rd argument) determines the \
precision of the final outcome. Execute HHL with fewer phase-estimation \
qubits:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"fd9a6466-7940-4cd0-b6e0-cfb3ae1e7777"],

